    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Popcorn! is a satisfying clicker game featuring levels with unique musical themes. Compete for high scores in the &quot;time trial&quot; mode, or enjoy the &quot;classic&quot; mode where there's no timer and no worries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twitch Integration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have your chatters join for a chance to be spawned as a popcorn kernel!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pop Against the Clock!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pop and eat popcorn as fast as you can and compete for high scores. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No timer, no worries. Just popping.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073930/extras/3efb0f5f6c16945ffe563939442b5d33.avif?t=1735006367\" width=616 height=363 /></span></p>",
